      Deprecated. 
      As of J2SE 5, use HIGH_SURROGATES, HIGH_PRIVATE_USE_SURROGATES, and LOW_SURROGATES. These new constants match the block definitions of the Unicode Standard. The of(char) and of(int) methods return the new constants, not SURROGATES_AREA.
